messages.message: It’s that time again. :slightly_smiling_face: The next code cut is this upcoming Monday Feb 8 for Release 21.2.0. This is a minor release. Please make sure to update and tag your JIRA’s as needed and add necessary release notes. JIRA board (https://instabase.atlassian.net/secure/RapidBoard.jspa?rapidView=104&projectKey=CDEP&quickFilter=294) is here and it’s looking quite empty.  Our UAT coordinator this month is Xi. Updates can be found on the <#CGQ7BD72A|> channel. And release tracker  (https://instabase.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/ENG/pages/935952396/Releases)info can be found here. Thanks all!
